Arkham: Revived is a custom authentication server for Batman: Arkham Origins Online.

The in-game store serves as an options menu.

All current progress will be replaced if successful.

774c23b3-8a63-46a7-b90d-e719b441a72b.description:

This action may be cancelled within 2 minutes.

955830ec-f0d8-40bf-b0dd-1d002d386a51.description:

They are not real items and cannot be used.

4a410e7a-c007-4aaf-8237-07d2ffe949c6.description:

This is the status code returned by the server, if it's not 1, then something went wrong.
